headline: 2 Healthcare Stocks on Our Watchlist and 1 We Brush Off
summary: From novel pharmaceuticals to telemedicine, most healthcare companies are on a mission to drive better patient outcomes. Players catalyzing medical advancements have benefited from elevated demand, and their momentum is only rising as the industry has posted a 15.6% gain over the past six months, beating the S&P 500 by 1.7 percentage points.
